sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Istio as Istio Gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Proxy as Model Registry Proxy<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (Istio mTLS)
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/5432 TCP
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Controller as ISVC Controller<br/>8081/TCP metrics
    participant CSI as CSI Storage Initializer
    participant Catalog as Catalog Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant CatalogDB as Catalog PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP
    participant HF as HuggingFace API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Job as Async Upload Job
    participant S3 as AWS S3<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OCI as OCI Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Sigstore as Sigstore<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client,DB: Flow 1: Model Registration via REST API

    Client->>Istio: POST /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/registered_models<br/>Auth: OAuth/OIDC
    Istio->>Proxy: Forward (Istio mTLS)<br/>AuthorizationPolicy enforced
    Proxy->>DB: INSERT via GORM<br/>Auth: Username/password<br/>Optional TLS
    DB-->>Proxy: Result
    Proxy-->>Istio: 201 Created (JSON)
    Istio-->>Client: Response

    Note over K8sAPI,Controller: Flow 2: InferenceService Sync (Controller)

    K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch InferenceService CRs<br/>TLS + ServiceAccount token
    Controller->>Proxy: PUT /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/inference_services<br/>HTTP :8080 Bearer token (optional)
    Proxy->>DB: Upsert metadata
    DB-->>Proxy: Result
    Proxy-->>Controller: 200 OK
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update ISVC labels/finalizers<br/>HTTPS/443 ServiceAccount token

    Note over CSI,Proxy: Flow 3: CSI Model Download

    Note right of CSI: KServe init container triggers<br/>model-registry:// URI
    CSI->>Proxy: GET /api/model_registry/v1alpha3/model_artifacts/{id}<br/>HTTP :8080 No auth
    Proxy->>DB: Query artifact URI
    DB-->>Proxy: Artifact location
    Proxy-->>CSI: Model artifact URI (S3/GCS/etc.)
    CSI->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 Provider-specific auth
    S3-->>CSI: Model files

    Note over Job,Sigstore: Flow 4: Async Model Upload Job

    Job->>S3: Download model files<br/>HTTPS/443 AWS IAM
    S3-->>Job: Model artifacts
    Job->>Sigstore: Sign model (Fulcio cert + Rekor log)<br/>HTTPS/443 Identity token
    Sigstore-->>Job: Signature + certificate
    Job->>OCI: Push model as OCI image (skopeo)<br/>HTTPS/443 Docker auth
    OCI-->>Job: Push confirmation
    Job->>Proxy: Register model/version/artifact<br/>HTTP(S) :8080/443 Bearer token
    Proxy->>DB: Insert metadata
    DB-->>Proxy: Result
    Proxy-->>Job: Registration complete

    Note over Catalog,HF: Flow 5: Catalog Model Sync

    Catalog->>CatalogDB: Acquire leader lock (pglock)<br/>PostgreSQL/5432 Username/password
    CatalogDB-->>Catalog: Lock acquired
    Catalog->>HF: GET /api/models (fetch metadata)<br/>HTTPS/443 Bearer token (HF_API_KEY)
    HF-->>Catalog: Model metadata
    Catalog->>CatalogDB: Upsert catalog entries<br/>PostgreSQL/5432 Username/password
    CatalogDB-->>Catalog: Stored
    Note right of Catalog: Also reads YAML ConfigMap<br/>sources via filesystem mount
